	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Me being a little on the ignorant side when it comes to electronics, is an open fuse just a bad fuse?  That was  10v power supply I am using that is giving me 22v on the famicom.  I just tried a 9v power supply I had and it gave me 14v.....what would be causing that?

		

